Peter Bromilow https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Peter_Bromilow 0 Peter Bromilow (21 April 1933 Cheshire, England - 16 October 1994 Los Angeles County, California) was a British-born actor.He made television guest appearances on Daniel Boone, The Virginian, The Feather and Father Gang, Remington Steele and The Wonder Years.
